plugin: manual
id: gnome-font-viewer
flags: simple
_description:
 PURPOSE:
       Check that gnome-font-viewer runs and works correctly
 STEPS:
      1. Run gnome-font-viewer icon. Does the icon look correct?
      2. Make sure "i" in a circle icon shows the info box
      3. Scroll through the fonts. Make sure they look different and they each have a title
      4. Click on a few different fonts and check for the page displaying well

unit: test plan
id: gnome-font-viewer-tp
name: gnome-font-viewer test plan
